1
00:00:02,290 --> 00:00:03,630
To everyone who came for me today,

2
00:00:03,630 --> 00:00:06,130
to all of you who made it out,
from the bottom of my heart...

3
00:00:25,830 --> 00:00:27,170
They've got some nerve showing up.

4
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:28,710
Why are they here together?

5
00:00:28,750 --> 00:00:30,040
That lawyer...
and the handsome president's wife.

6
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:31,380
Something scandalous happened between them, right?

7
00:00:32,380 --> 00:00:33,380
Welcome, everyone.

8
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:35,710
Alright, everyone.

9
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:37,540
Please direct your attention to the screen.

10
00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:39,670
I've compiled my greatest achievements

11
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:41,000
into a special video presentation.

12
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:42,420
Please enjoy.

13
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:48,540
Huh? What is this?

14
00:00:48,790 --> 00:00:49,830
Why is he with all those women?

15
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,630
Oh my god.

16
00:00:50,630 --> 00:00:53,750
No way.

17
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:55,380
Is something wrong?

18
00:00:56,130 --> 00:00:57,130
Huh?

19
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:58,880
This isn't the video
of my achievements.

20
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:00,710
It's some other weird video.

21
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:02,290
Hahahahaha!

22
00:01:02,330 --> 00:01:03,960
This is a disaster.

23
00:01:04,420 --> 00:01:06,130
Hey, turn it off!

24
00:01:06,830 --> 00:01:07,830
Now!

25
00:01:11,330 --> 00:01:13,580
Turn the video off now!

26
00:01:14,420 --> 00:01:15,320
You're the absolute worst.

27
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:16,750
He's a serial abuser of power.

28
00:01:16,790 --> 00:01:17,920
That so-called handsome president.

29
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,500
The second he opens his mouth, he's calling someone an idiot.

30
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:21,290
Moron, klutz, imbecile.

31
00:01:21,290 --> 00:01:22,750
Monkey, gorilla, chimpanzee.

32
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,880
These personal attacks
are infuriating.

33
00:01:25,330 --> 00:01:26,330
I'll never forgive him.

34
00:01:26,330 --> 00:01:27,330
That guy...

35
00:01:27,670 --> 00:01:30,460
No, hahahahaha!

36
00:01:33,210 --> 00:01:34,210
No.

37
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,710
That's not real.

38
00:01:37,380 --> 00:01:39,380
It's all fake!

39
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:41,420
He's had plastic surgery.

40
00:01:43,710 --> 00:01:44,330
Huh?

41
00:01:44,330 --> 00:01:46,670
He looks totally different.

42
00:01:46,670 --> 00:01:47,880
It looks so fake.

43
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,460
I knew it.

44
00:01:49,630 --> 00:01:51,960
So that's it.
He's not even handsome.

45
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,080
No!

46
00:01:53,670 --> 00:01:56,210
No, no, no!
No, no, no!!
